2. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - One of the applications mentioned in the paper is security, which falls under the domain of cryptography and security. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a supervised learning method for wireless localisation, which is a key aspect of machine learning. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The proposed approach involves the use of machine learning algorithms, which is a key aspect of artificial intelligence. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The proposed approach involves the use of wireless signals to detect anomalies, which can be seen as a control system.
